  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="postcard">
        <head>
          <note place="left">
            <l>ROMA</l>
            <l>Reconciliation Street and St. Peter.</l>
            <l>Rue de la Conciliation et St. Pierre.</l>
            <l>Conciliazione Strasse und Hg. Peters-kirche.</l>
          </note>
        </head>
        <opener>
          <salute>Dear Mrs. Parks,</salute>
        </opener>
        <p>We are having a wonderful experience touring Europe. Hope things are going well with you. I am thinking of you constantly. Will see you soon.</p>
        <closer>
          <salute></salute>
          <signed>M.L. King</signed>
        </closer>
      </div>
    </body>
